      <body>
         <pb n="1" facs="../images/ew_b5_1580_001.jpg"/>
        <!-- <div> -->
            <opener>               
               <dateline>
                  <span style="text-align: right"><name type="place" subtype="building"><choice><abbr>Fla.</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice> State <choice><abbr>Hospt.</abbr><expan>Hospital</expan></choice><location><geo>30.706597 -84.841442</geo></location></name></span><lb/>
                  <name type="place" subtype="city">Chattahoochee, <choice><abbr>Fla</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice></name><lb/>
                  <date when="1929-04-10"><choice><abbr>4 - 10 - 29</abbr><expan>April 10, 1929</expan></choice></date><lb/>
                  
             </dateline>
          
               <salute>
                  Dear <name type="person">Miss White</name>:<lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener> 
         
            <p style="text-indent">
               Only a few lines<lb/>
               to let you hear from me. This<lb/>
               leaves me well hoping that this<lb/>
               will find you well.<lb/>
            </p>
         
            <p style="text-indent"><name type="person">Miss White</name><choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> I am very<lb/>
               anxious to get back home. And<lb/>
               if you will get in touch with the<lb/>               <choice><sic>Superintendant</sic><corr>superintendent</corr></choice> and see about<lb/>
               getting me out<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> I will pay you<lb/>
               <choice><orig>what ever</orig><reg>whatever</reg></choice> the cost is when I get<lb/>
               home. And I do wish that you see<lb/>
               about my things and take charge<lb/>
               of them until I get back.<lb/>
            </p>
         
            <p style="text-indent">
               This is the <choice><abbr>Supt.</abbr><expan>superintendent's</expan></choice> address<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>:</reg></choice><lb/>
               <name type="person">Dr. J. Q. Folmar</name>, <name type="place" subtype="address"><choice><abbr>Fla.</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice> State <choice><abbr>Hospt.</abbr><expan>Hospital</expan></choice><location><geo>30.706597 -84.841442</geo></location></name><choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
            </p>
            <p style="text-indent">
               <choice><orig>you</orig><reg>You</reg></choice> must not believe anything<lb/>
               wrong of me<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> for I am the same as when<lb/>
               you first<choice><sic>.</sic><corr/></choice> <supplied reason="omitted-in-original">met</supplied> me<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> Tell my pastor <choice><abbr>&amp;</abbr><expan>and</expan></choice> <choice><orig>Deacon</orig><reg>deacon</reg></choice> to do all they<lb/>
               can for me.
            </p>

            <closer style="text-align: center">
               <salute>
                  <choice><orig>your</orig><reg>Your</reg></choice> sister in Christ<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice><lb/>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">Sarah Best</name><choice><orig>.</orig><reg/></choice><lb/>
               </signed>
            </closer>

